flowchart TD
    A[Start: business question] --> B[Clarify question and assumptions]
    B --> C[Identify decision this analysis supports]
    C --> D[Break into 2 to 5 sub-questions]
    D --> E[Write testable hypotheses: primary, alternatives, null]
    E --> F[Define confirm and refute criteria]
    F --> G[List required tables, metrics, window, segments]
    G --> H[Set scope: in and out]
    H --> I[Rate plan quality: Ready, Needs Work, Blocked]
    I --> J[Write plan.md with flow diagram]
    J --> K[Checkpoint: proceed to Data QA?]
